data.description: Price recently reduced!! Welcome to 531 Ballentine Avenue! This charming house is now available for sale in Marion City. With 2 bedrooms 1 bathroom, this property offers a cozy and comfortable living space. The home spans across 1360 square feet, providing ample room for you and your loved ones. Originally built in 1930, the home exudes character and potential. Each bedroom and the living room are equipped with ceiling fans to help keep you cool during warmer months. The master bedroom was originally designed as two separate rooms, allowing for easy conversion back to create a total of 3 bedrooms in the home if desired. Inside the house, you'll discover hardwood floors throughout, adding warmth and charm to the living spaces.
